00:00:02.882 --> 00:00:03.738
Since when do you 

00:00:03.739 --> 00:00:04.881
read physical newspapers?

00:00:04.882 --> 00:00:05.841
It’s retro, you know

00:00:05.842 --> 00:00:06.761
So, what’s happened?

00:00:06.762 --> 00:00:07.973
Germany's largest state 

00:00:07.974 --> 00:00:09.084
has banned the use of 

00:00:09.085 --> 00:00:10.601
non-binary language in schools,

00:00:10.602 --> 00:00:11.370
high schools and 

00:00:11.371 --> 00:00:12.321
