00:00:22.995 --> 00:00:24.358
There are different variations, 

00:00:24.359 --> 00:00:25.681
but people often use an asterisk,

00:00:25.682 --> 00:00:26.815
a colon or an underscore 

00:00:26.816 --> 00:00:27.949
to combine the masculine 

00:00:27.950 --> 00:00:28.721
and feminine form

00:00:28.722 --> 00:00:29.674
