00:00:29.675 --> 00:00:31.201
both women and non-binary people

00:00:31.202 --> 00:00:31.902
And why do they 

00:00:31.903 --> 00:00:32.561
want to ban that?

00:00:32.562 --> 00:00:33.675
Bavaria’s government says 

00:00:33.676 --> 00:00:34.531
“language has to be 

00:00:34.532 --> 00:00:35.561
