00:00:35.562 --> 00:00:36.374
Surely there are 

00:00:36.375 --> 00:00:37.761
bigger problems in the world?

00:00:37.762 --> 00:00:38.733
You might want to know that 

00:00:38.734 --> 00:00:39.081
the use of

00:00:39.082 --> 00:00:40.503
gender-neutral language in schools

00:00:40.504 --> 00:00:41.601
and official communications

00:00:41.602 --> 00:00:42.616
has become a big debate 

00:00:42.617 --> 00:00:43.801
in other countries as well,

00:00:43.802 --> 00:00:45.081
including France and Argentina,

00:00:45.082 --> 00:00:46.081
with advocates saying

00:00:46.082 --> 00:00:47.586
that language has always adapted 

00:00:47.587 --> 00:00:49.001
to social and technical changes,

00:00:49.002 --> 00:00:50.115
and critics saying it 

00:00:50.116 --> 00:00:51.642
threatens clarity and tradition 

00:00:51.643 --> 00:00:52.991
Right, sometimes I do miss 

00:00:52.992 --> 00:00:54.534
